2. 在 [Linux Foundation](https://www.linuxfoundation.org/)  舉辦的 [LinuxCon Japan 2016](http://events.linuxfoundation.org/events/archive/2016/linuxcon-japan) (7 月/日本) 發表 Linux container 成果 (高魁良)
    * 講題: [Dynamically Hacking the Kernel with Containers](https://events.linuxfoundation.org/sites/events/files/slides/talk_7.pdf)
3. 在開源機器人領域最頂級的研討會 [ROScon 2016](http://roscon.ros.org/2016/) (10 月/韓國) 發表低成本自走車 (鄭聖文等人)
    * 講題: [
Realtime autonomous car for studying and ROS2 cross compiling](https://www.slideshare.net/shengwen1997/ros2-cross-compiling)
