    * 講題: [Effectively Measure and Reduce Kernel Latencies for Real-time Constraints](https://events.linuxfoundation.org/sites/events/files/slides/ELC2017-%20Effectively%20Measure%20and%20Reduce%20Kernel%20Latencies%20for%20Real-time%20Constraints%20%281%29.pdf)

# 開發新的開放原始碼專案
1. [Puyuma](https://github.com/Puyuma): 低價低功耗完全開放原始程式碼的無人車解決方案
    * 展示影片: [Lane following](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=84MXc0_F61o) ; [Lane visualization](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XK602hzbORY)
2. [F9 microkernel](https://github.com/f9micro): 兼顧安全和效能的 IoT 作業系統核心
3. [mini-arm-os](https://github.com/jserv/mini-arm-os): 具體而微的教學用作業系統核心
4. [AMaCC](https://github.com/jserv/amacc): 世界最小適用於 ARM 架構的 C 語言編譯器 (可自我編譯)
5. [Dozen Cloud](http://dozencloud.org/): 適用於 ARM 的 OpenStack 基礎建設

# 貢獻到上游開放原始碼專案
* [HackMD](https://hackmd.io): Realtime collaborative markdown notes on all platforms.
* [OPIC](https://github.com/dryman/opic): serialize/deserialize primitive types as well as general abstract data types (和 Google 工程師合作)
* [Chewing](https://github.com/chewing): 新酷音輸入法計畫，全球區指可數依循中華民國(台灣)教育部規範的中文輸入法系統，多款 Linux 發行套件內建的繁體中文輸入法程式。Chrome OS 內建。

